以 ' ,row_number() over (order by dfg_service_ticket.id desc) as rn from dfg_service_ticket left join f_code_service pay_type on pay' 开头的 标识符 太长。最大长度为 128。
字符串 ' ,row_number() over (order by dfg_service_ticket.id desc) as rn from dfg_service_ticket left join f_code_service pay_type on pay_' 后的引号不完整。
